## 11. Android NDK Notes

- Place your C++ under `app/src/main/cpp/`
- In `CMakeLists.txt` (Android), add `add_library(MyEngine SHARED ...)` instead of `add_executable`
- Bundle `libcurl` as a prebuilt `.a` for Android (use `curl-android` from GitHub)
- Call `AppInit()` from JNI:

```cpp
extern "C" JNIEXPORT void JNICALL
Java_com_yourapp_MainActivity_nativeInit(JNIEnv*, jobject) {
    AppInit();
}
```

