## 12. Architecture Diagram

```
DataModel*
├── Game
├── Players
│     └── Player { name, userId, x, y, z }
└── ExampleService

ServerModel*
├── ServerStorage      (key-value store)
├── ServerScriptService (named script registry)
└── NetworkHandle
      ├── Connect()       → POST /
      ├── PlayerPacket()  → POST /Packet
      └── TriggerBan()    → POST /Ban
```

