## Extending the Handle

To add more endpoints, just add a method to `NetworkHandle`:

```cpp
// Example: POST /Event { name, data }
void FireEvent(const std::string& eventName, const json& payload, ResponseCallback cb);
```

This keeps the pointer chain clean:
```
ServerModel → Handle → FireEvent(...)
```

